{"id": "art-230", "label": "Art. 230", "title": "Art. 230", "slug": "art-230", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 230 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_566981578\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1893\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_566981578\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> în\nnume colectiv, <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> cu\nr&#259;spundere limitat&#259;, dac&#259; un asociat decedeaz&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dac&#259; nu exist&#259; <span class=SpellE>conven&#355;ie</span>\ncontrar&#259;, societatea trebuie s&#259; pl&#259;teasc&#259; partea ce se\ncuvine <span class=SpellE>mo&#351;tenitorilor</span>, dup&#259; ultimul <span\nclass=SpellE>bilan&#355;</span> contabil aprobat, în termen de 3 luni de la\nnotificarea decesului asociatului, dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>r&#259;ma&#351;i</span> nu prefer&#259; s&#259; continue\nsocietatea cu <span class=SpellE>mo&#351;tenitorii</span> care consimt la\naceasta.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Prevederile alin. (1) se\naplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nîn comandit&#259; simpl&#259;, în caz de deces al unuia dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>comandita&#355;i</span>,\nîn afar&#259; de cazul când <span class=SpellE>mo&#351;tenitorii</span>\ns&#259;i nu prefer&#259; s&#259; r&#259;mân&#259; în societate în aceast&#259;\ncalitate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Mo&#351;tenitorii</span>\nr&#259;mân r&#259;spunz&#259;tori, potrivit art. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>224</span><span style='color:black'>, pân&#259; la publicarea\nschimb&#259;rilor intervenite.</span></p>"}